        <title>Setup record</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/p/setup-record/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/p/setup-record/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/p/setup-record/pawel-czerwinski-8uZPynIu-rQ-unsplash.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Setup record" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;This article records how I setup the Blog with a Hugo theme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Refer to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/getting-started/quick-start/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://gohugo.io/getting-started/quick-start/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://space.bilibili.com/3546647648799599/search/video?keyword=hugo&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://space.bilibili.com/3546647648799599/search/video?keyword=hugo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;prerequisiteswindows&#34;&gt;Prerequisites(Windows):
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install Git;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install Go;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install Hugo extend version;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get a github account, and create a repo for the blog.(&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/wujiaforward/wujiaforward.github.io&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/wujiaforward/wujiaforward.github.io&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;commandline-worksbuild-the-blog-based-on-hugo-theme-stackexamplesite&#34;&gt;Commandline works(build the blog based on hugo-theme-stack/exampleSite):
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;I used GitBash for the flowing setup commandline works.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;hugo new site &amp;lt;folder_name_for_your_blog&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;cd &amp;lt;folder_name_for_your_blog&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;git init&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;git submodule add &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack.git&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack.git&lt;/a&gt; &amp;lt;themes/hugo-theme-stack&amp;gt;&lt;br&gt;
// maybe just don&amp;rsquo;t need the &amp;lt;&amp;gt; part in a more simple way. Need to change the flowing steps, check later.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;themes/hugo-theme-stack: cp -r archetypes/ assets/ data/ i18n/ images/ layouts/ config.yaml &amp;lt;folder_name_for_your_blog&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;themes/hugo-theme-stack/exampleSite: cp -r content/ hugo.yaml .gitignore &amp;lt;folder_name_for_your_blog&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;hugo server -D&lt;br&gt;
// check if the setup is OK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;deploy the blog with githubpages. (&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/hosting-and-deployment/hosting-on-github/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://gohugo.io/hosting-and-deployment/hosting-on-github/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;中文也可以吗？？&lt;/p&gt;</description>
        </item>
